            </picture>
            <article class="hero-section__content">
                <div class="hero-section__content-header">
                    <div class="c-approved-by">
                        <ul>
                            <li><img src="sections/new/hero-section/images/approved-by-1.webp" alt="Dr. Shah" /></li>
                            <li><img src="sections/new/hero-section/images/approved-by-2.webp" alt="Dr. Maxfield" /></li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>Approved by <strong>Dr. Shah</strong> &amp; <strong>Dr. Maxfield</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <h1>5 Reasons Micro-Infusion Is the Smarter Alternative to Expensive Creams</h1>
                    <p><strong>Finally:</strong> A painless, sterile, at-home treatment that targets wrinkles and dark spots… even when skincare stops working.</p>
                </div>
